{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For a special legacy, you are returning to the island where you grew up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your family worked their entire lives for this beach. Acquired with big dreams, this beach presents an opportunity to keep their memory alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is now in your hands to take the beach to the top and transform it into an unforgettable vacation paradise for customers. However, it won't be easy. A journey full of surprises awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/drown.gif?t=1728923688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>From Zero to Hero: A Magical Island Adventure</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run the first and only beach on the island! Work smart and enjoy the sea and the sand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design and develop your beach however you want with unique beach objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can design your beach sign and set regular and VIP entrance fees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can increase your popularity by valuing your customers' comments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/car.gif?t=1728923688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can earn palm trees by completing level quests in the progress tab and spend them in the skills tab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can flirt with women and start a relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover treasures hidden deep in the sea with your detector! Sell your findings at auctions for the highest bid and become wealthy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Organize events at your desired times and design special areas. Immerse yourself in the Beach Club spirit with speakers, lighting, and a foam machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Mafia Poses the Biggest Threat to the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The sea is infested with dangerous sharks that could snatch a swimming customer at any moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Criminals may infiltrate your beach and try to secretly take photos of your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your customers Could Drown In the Sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can either protect your beach from all these dangers or abandon it to its fate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All the Apps You Need Are At Your Fingertips!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the Map app to avoid getting lost on the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place all your orders through Betrendy and wait for your delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Share photos On Onstagram.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase music from Sotify and enjoy playing it on your beach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Participate in surprise auctions or start your own with the Trader app.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Track your employees and their salaries, your menu and prices, payments, and everything else related to your beach with the MyBeach app.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you earn money, you can buy luxury cars and sell them through negotiations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Approaching the top, you can discover alternative ways to earn money and purchase the yacht and mansion of your dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/yacht.gif?t=1728923688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Will you be able to fulfill your family's unfinished dreams?</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728923688","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/page.bg.jpg?t=1728923688","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728923688","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728923688","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"There is no nudity in the game.\r\nNon-nudity sexual events are handled in a humorous way.\r\nThe game DOES NOT include any events of these, such as sexual assault/non-consensual sex, drug abuse, self-harm, or suicide."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For a special legacy, you are returning to the island where you grew up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your family worked their entire lives for this beach. Acquired with big dreams, this beach presents an opportunity to keep their memory alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is now in your hands to take the beach to the top and transform it into an unforgettable vacation paradise for customers. However, it won't be easy. A journey full of surprises awaits 